    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways! I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I\u2019ve priced it to move. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a well-maintained A80 chassis featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six. This example retains its factory-spec sequential turbocharger configuration and is paired with the robust V160 Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Power is managed through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, providing excellent lateral grip and exit speed. The vehicle features a stock double-wishbone suspension setup that remains taut and responsive. Recent service includes a full timing belt replacement, new valve cover gaskets, and a comprehensive cooling system flush. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are strong, with consistent compression across all cylinders and smooth gear synchronization.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Functional interior and exterior.",
