    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presented in excellent overall shape, this vehicle is a testament to meticulous care. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with only minor, negligible imperfections consistent with light use. Step inside to find a pristine, non-smoker cabin where the seats remain firm and the surfaces are free of any significant wear or blemishes. Mechanically, the car is in top form; it has been serviced regularly, starts instantly, and delivers a smooth, responsive driving experience. All features, from the climate control to the infotainment system, operate perfectly. This is a dependable, well-presented car ready for its next owner to drive away with total peace of mind.",
