    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it's looking for a brand new adventure! It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and it honestly still drives like a dream. If you're looking for a solid, dependable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
