      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain offers immediate throttle response and mechanical transparency. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including reinforced rear subframe mounts and a cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension deliver precise turn-in and predictable lateral grip. A mechanically robust example ready for spirited canyon runs.",
